    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"307953\">Ruben Van de Velde</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/113489-new-members/topic/can't.20seem.20to.20specialise.20a.20universally.20quantified.20hypothesis/near/480515515\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>You can write <code>hy 1 x1 x3</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Chapter 4 of Mechanics of Proof introduces new syntax without explaining it - or requires us to find out ourselves.</p>\n<p>Perhaps that's part of the educational challenge...</p>",
